kieker.tools.traceAnalysis.filter.visualization.graph

类 CompleteOriginRetentionPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • kieker.tools.traceAnalysis.filter.visualization.graph.AbstractOriginRetentionPolicy
      • kieker.tools.traceAnalysis.filter.visualization.graph.CompleteOriginRetentionPolicy
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IOriginRetentionPolicy

    public final class CompleteOriginRetentionPolicy
extends AbstractOriginRetentionPolicy
    The complete origin retention policy represents the intention that every origin should be retained in the graph model and corresponds to the kind OriginRetentionPolicyKind.ALL. Be aware that this policy may lead to extensive resource consumption when processing vast logs.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.6
    作者:
    Holger Knoche

      • uniteWith

        public IOriginRetentionPolicy uniteWith(IOriginRetentionPolicy other)
        从接口复制的说明: IOriginRetentionPolicy
        Unites this retention policy with another one and returns the resulting policy. Note that the resulting policy is not necessarily one of the original policies.
        参数:
        other - The retention policy to unite this policy with
        返回:
        The resulting policy, which may be a completely new object
